@page "/careers"
@layout PublicLayout

<PageTitle>Careers - grow.IT</PageTitle>

<div class="contact-page footer-info-page">
    <section class="contact-hero">
        <span class="contact-kicker">Careers</span>
        <h1>Build software that makes mission work easier to prove.</h1>
        <p>Grow.IT needs people who care about simple language, durable systems, data quality, and tools that reduce administrative pressure on founders.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="contact-form-section">
        <article class="contact-form-card">
            <h2>Current openings</h2>
            <p>We do not have public roles posted right now. We still welcome thoughtful introductions from product, engineering, implementation, nonprofit operations, and customer success professionals who understand mission-led work.</p>
            <p>When we hire, we look for people who can make complex operational workflows feel clear, useful, and respectful to the founder using them.</p>
        </article>
    </section>

    <section class="contact-grid-section">
        <div class="contact-grid">
            <article class="contact-card">
                <h2>Product</h2>
                <p>Design workflows that help founders answer simple questions and get useful reports back.</p>
            </article>
            <article class="contact-card">
                <h2>Engineering</h2>
                <p>Build reliable data, permissions, reporting, export, and integration foundations.</p>
            </article>
            <article class="contact-card">
                <h2>Implementation</h2>
                <p>Help organizations set up clean records, team roles, reporting routines, and readiness goals.</p>
            </article>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="contact-cta">
        <div class="contact-cta-card">
            <h2>Interested in future roles?</h2>
            <p>Send your background, what you are strong at, and why this mission matters to you.</p>
            <div class="contact-cta-actions">
                <a href="/contact?subject=Career%20Interest" class="btn btn-primary">Submit Interest</a>
                <a href="/about" class="btn btn-outline">About Grow.IT</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</div>
